ygData.subject: Way to Faydwer
ygData.msgSnippet: There is a canoe that takes you from the main land of Odus ( i think its called) to the Kerran isle. Has anyone tried taking this canoe all the way to Faydwer?
ygData.messageBody:
There is a canoe that takes you from the main land of Odus ( i think
its called) to the Kerran isle.
Has anyone tried taking this canoe all the way to Faydwer?
If the world wraps around, theoretically you could continue past the
Kerran Isle and eventually hit Faydwer.
Then again, maybe Norrath is flat and we'll fall off the edge into a
deep pit where sea monkeys will rescue us only to sacrifice us to their
almighty God, Bullwinkle.

Ok, sorry about that, too much coffee.

Anyway, has anyone tried this?

Bathory
Cazic-Thule
